{"id": "art-701", "label": "Art. 701", "title": "Art. 701", "slug": "art-701", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1018147088\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2421\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1018147088\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 70<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_258184001\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2420\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_258184001\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Actele de <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ie</span> asupra\nbunurilor unei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> pot fi încheiate\nîn temeiul puterilor conferite <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ilor</span>\nlegali ai <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, dup&#259; caz, prin <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>, actul constitutiv sau\nhot&#259;rârile organelor statutare ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nadoptate în conformitate cu prevederile prezentei <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legi</i> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ale actului constitutiv al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, nefiind necesar&#259; o procur&#259;\nspecial&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în form&#259; autentic&#259; în\nacest scop, chiar dac&#259; actele de <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ie</span>\ntrebuie încheiate în form&#259; autentic&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}